item.title: Strength in Data: Connecting to the Taskmaster Database
item.description: Your Task Successfully connect to the Taskmaster database from within R. Fastest wins; your time starts now! Introduction and Objective This article provides an overview of Trabajo de las Mesas, a pivotal Taskmaster database that will be central to performing a multitude of analysis and questions that we may want to answer regarding Taskmaster. TOC The article will also provide guidance on how to connect to the database from within .
